  <brief_title>Foot Controlled Robotic Endoscope Enabled Robot FESS</brief_title>
  <official_title>Safety and Feasibility Study of the Foot Controlled Robotic Endoscope Enabled Robot (FREE) in Functional Endoscopic Sinus Surgery</official_title>
